<C>__{doctor parnassus }
<D>__{i want you to relax and try as far as possible to think of nothing.}
<C>__{george}
<D>__{that's not difficult... in my condition.}
<A>__{doctor parnassus closes his eyes. he seems to be making an effort.}
<C>__{doctor parnassus}
<D>__{hold your breath.}
<A>__{george does so.}
<C>__{doctor parnassus }
<D>__{very good, very good. yes... yes, i see... i see... very interesting.}
<A>__{doctor parnassus takes his hand from george's head and gives the contraption back to percy.}
