<C>__{doctor parnassus}
<D>__{anthony shepherd.}
<C>__{tony}
<P>__{(stunned)}
<D>__{my god! that's it! you're right! anthony shepherd! they call me tony. tony shepherd! that's who i am!}
<A>__{valentina and anton begin to pay attention and gather around.}
