<P>__{(dismissively)}
<D>__{it's an ancient technique of mental divination, but i'm very rusty and it doesn't always work satisfactorily.}
<C>__{tony}
<D>__{but that's amazing! brilliant!}
<P>__{(oddly concerned)}
<D>__{was there anything else?}
<A>__{doctor parnassus shakes his head, no.}
<C>__{tony }
