<P>__{(sarcastic)}
<D>__{oh dear, was that a rude question? have i put my foot in it?}
<C>__{tony}
<D>__{that's so strange. and horrible.. it's a complete blank. but i do remember i was involved in some sort of charity.. trying to do good, to make the world a better place, you know...inspire people, give them hope....}
<P>__{(self deprecatingly)}
<D>__{what an arrogant idiot.}
